    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS, providing a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, and the chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under load. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment, rod bearing replacement for longevity, and a refreshed cooling system. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension utilizes original geometry with fresh bushings for a communicative, analog driving experience. This is a collector-grade specimen with documented service history and flawless mechanical synchronization.",
      "price": 48500.0,
