    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that serves as a benchmark for the 'mint' standard. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior paint is entirely original and boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional multi-stage paint correction and ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new. The leather upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one, and the dashboard is free of any UV degradation. Every switch, dial, and digital interface operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a complete, chronological service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a show-ready standard, showing no signs of heat-cycling or fluid leaks. This sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and all factory manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
