      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car has been pampered, garage-kept, and is in such incredible shape that it still smells fresh. It drives perfectly and looks stunning from every angle\u2014not a single blemish to be found. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. Drop me a message if you want to come see it in person; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
